Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[classical music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Delete!\N-[man screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[man groaning and choking in agony]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[narrator] The average Japanese adult\Nwould say that Teru Mikami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was a child\Nwith a strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was able to distinguish right\Nfrom wrong better than any of his peers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And compared to\Nthe average Japanese person,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru had been through\Nand seen far worse miseries...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and even witnessed death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[classical music continues playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,SELECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[alarm clock beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping outside]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[kids laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] In this world,\Nthere is only good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one of the first universal truths\NI grasped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,from observing the world around me\Nwhen I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Every human being, without exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ends up falling into one category\Nor the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in those innocent years\Nof elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,one could not escape that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,CLASS REP. THIRD-YEAR GROUP A\NTERU MIKAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As class president, I strived to achieve\Ngreat things for my fellow students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But there were always enemies,\Ngood against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop! Let go of me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[kids laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil has to be confronted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-[pencil snaps]\N-[boy] Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There were times when it seemed\Nevil would triumph over good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter what happened to me,\NI felt happy for one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffing] Thank you, Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing those words of gratitude\Nfrom the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,made me want to save them again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason,\NI never spared any effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to stand up for\Nmy sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[kids laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah! Do it!\N-Does this bug you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[kid laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[nervous laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that was only true\Nin the world of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle school was another matter entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I confronted evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the more enemies I had to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[crunching]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Victims would become participants,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the people watching\Nwould be influenced by evil
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and become enemies themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But for justice to triumph,\Nit requires action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I realized, to serve justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to delete evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The only person who understood my hopes\Nand remained my ally
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,was the woman who raised me on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, rather, it used to be my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru, not everything in the world\Nis going to work the way you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you\Nto suffer so much for your beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're proving\Ngetting hurt like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is plain foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to realize that some things\Nwill never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] My mother was wrong.\NShe didn't side with justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She was one of those\Nwho deserved to be deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] That was when the miracle happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[car crashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Four of the worst delinquents\Nfrom my school
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,lost control of their car\Nwhile they were joy-riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One bystander was killed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That bystander was my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In one fell swoop,\Nall the people I resented
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,had been deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop shivering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, it hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With these people out of the picture,\Nhow many others would benefit as a result?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, their victims were relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But, beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't everyone in my class\Nbe happier now that they were gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And sure enough, I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our classroom\Nbecame a peaceful, joyful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There will always be consequences\Nfor evil deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the way the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The way it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil must be deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] Now then, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any more problems\Nwith these records?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-[man] No, they're fine.\N-[Teru] With every passing year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,my commitment to justice\Nonly grew stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that there will always be those\Nwho have no reason to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those whose very existence\Nis a threat to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the closer they grew to adulthood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the less likely it was\Nthat they would ever reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They could only be deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysteriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,every time I judge someone as evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they would soon be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I special somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine judgment\Nmust be brought upon evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it isn't, then someone must\Ntake it upon themselves to punish evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,COURTHOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I became a prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,GUIDE TO JAPANESE SENTENCING
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the role of the prosecutor\Nto see that evil is brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an ideal job for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,God came before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,MASS MURDER OF VICIOUS CRIMINALS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that had been happening\Naround me wasn't coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,WHO IS THE CRIMINAL KILLER, KIRA?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was divine justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,God had been watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God had seen\Nhow I did not surrender to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He reached out his hand\Nand punished the evil people for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I realized that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to frequent places\Nwhere God was bound to be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[ominous music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,God recognized me, as I had always hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but He found me worthy\Nof sharing His power to eliminate evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, it doesn't matter\Nif I can't hear His voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall figure out what Kira wants\Nand carry out His will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete. Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete. Delete. Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete. Delete. Delete. Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[rapid typing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Mikami made the choice\Nto kill Demegawa himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I never requested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An understandable move\Nbut now there's no spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira needs a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment,\NI can't make any moves myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What will he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] Kira isn't saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be in a situation\Nwhere he can't move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is an important time for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a spokesperson\Nto spread His word to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will take the initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-[door opening]\N-[men] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra, extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a new development\Nin the Kira case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's chosen a new spokesperson\Nto take Demegawa's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[upbeat music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi Takada!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kiyomi Takada from News 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, it will be my duty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to spread the word of Kira,\Naccurately and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, NHN will fairly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] So he picked\NNHN's star newscaster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's got good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Choosing Takki was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] ...will be passed onto him\Nthrough me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the girl\Nthat Light dated in university.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've moved quickly, Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it won't take them long\Nto find the connection between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which could be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, on second thought,\Nshe's not a bad choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one I never would have considered,\Nsince I already knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This could actually make things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can definitely use her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll have to find a way\Nto contact her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a chance to meet her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was on a debate program\Nshe was hosting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a shrewd and fair host\Nfor the most part,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but her attitude changed suddenly\Nwhen Kira's name was mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a uniquely rigid sense of justice\Nthat I could identify with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She hates crimes and social evils\Nwith a passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked with her privately\Nseveral times after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She clearly supports Kira,\Nbut it's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks like Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes her the broadcaster most worthy\Nof being the new voice of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be too suspicious for Kira\Nto choose an ex-girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as his representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's been no sign of Light\Nsending her any messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm thinking about this too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I just had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking we could make use\Nof Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in university, she and I\Nwere actually dating for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] So, he admits it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no intention\Nto hide the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's acting as his spokesperson,\Nshe must be receiving orders from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in contact with Kira somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think our best bet\Nis to use that connection
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to find a way to Kira through her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,KIYOMI TAKADA CHOSEN AS\NKIRA'S SPOKESPERSON
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Takki's probably doing it\Nbecause Kira's threatening her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be too scared to help us out\Nwith our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know her current cellphone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that I'll be able\Nto convince her once we get talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll meet with me, if I ask her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to this guy! You're the man, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking to her will be easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but the real challenge will be to get her\Nto help us find and arrest Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to talk about a lot of\Ndifferent topics while we were in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And one thing was clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-She worships Kira.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But we might be able\Nto use that to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The police claim they support Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but aren't doing anything\None way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll reveal that I've joined the police
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask her what we can do\Nto help Kira further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To her, it will sound like a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can convince her to assist us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as we pretend\Nit's for Kira's benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that will go over well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely sure,\Nbut it's worth a try at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. It would be foolish for us\Nto pass up a lead like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll call her tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[men] Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, I'd like to listen in\Non your conversation with Ms. Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's better if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If she lets slip something about Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be best if more than one of us\Nwas listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Kiyomi? This is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Hi, it's been a while.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi, I have something important\Nto tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we meet somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know my timing is pretty bad. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the woman the whole world\Nis watching right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so it might not be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Don't play innocent and humble\Nwith me, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have called if you didn't\Nthink it was possible to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] You're right.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you again,\Nbut I never had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it looks like\Nour jobs have brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After so much time,\Nour paths are about to cross again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me crazy\Nbut I feel like this is fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "our jobs"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'm working with the police now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was part of what I wanted\Nto talk to you about... in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] The police aren't doing anything\Nto defy Kira at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I may be able to help you,\Ndepending on what you're asking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I just want you\Nto hear what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere. Just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After tonight's broadcast has finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll book a hotel room for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] A hotel room? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The last I heard,\Nyou were still living with Miss Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are things not going too well\Non the home front?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Well, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa's just not intelligent enough\Nto be my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Misa] Mochi.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cooking is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I appreciate that you're doing\Neverything for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-but it's been five days now.\N-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Light doesn't know about you\Nhanging around all the time, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to get a really bad feeling\Nabout this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh huh...\N-I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Light trusts me totally,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't you think most people\Nwould start saying I'm cheating on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he'd be so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Near and the others told me\Nthat this woman's supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But could it really be\Nthis unbelievably stupid girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[crunching]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Kira still hasn't tried\Nto contact me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's in a situation where he's\Nunable to contact me even if he wants to,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then the next best thing would be\Nfor him to contact Takada instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Good evening.\NThis is the nine o'clock news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I have an announcement\Nthat comes directly from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His words are to become\Nthe new law of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira will never forgive those people\Nwhose existence is a threat to justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but he will also not forgive those\Nwho live wastefully
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and refuse to use their abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to contribute\Nto the betterment of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kira's gonna kill lazy people now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You're taking this too far,\NMikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to be making\Nthose kinds of statements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get a hold of him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Audio and video online.\NNo blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Until next time.\N-The nine o'clock news is just ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's in order.\NI'll head back to HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps leaving]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opening and closing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[door creaking open]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft classical music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[both exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Oh. I'm sorry, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't seem like that long\Nsince we last saw each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is Light doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If he just stays silent,\Nshe'll get suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't tell me\Nyou've never been in love before, Ide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The mood's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone vibrating]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasps] Kira…\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She just said it's Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's contacting her directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Um, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? No, I'm with a friend right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If luck is on my side,\NI can get on the phone myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mikami, can you make it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] He wanted to meet me\Nall of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] Someone who requests\Na private meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with Kira's spokesperson?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak with him, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he wants to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to choose you, Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's passed the phone to Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be dangerous\Nif he's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[distorted voice] Who am I speaking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Five pages on November 26?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it. What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing well, Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just see how much\Nyou can figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] God, you're not free\Nto speak right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being watched at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But how I can trust\Nyou're the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he asking me\Nto judge someone right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn to Sakura TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Sakura TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll invite Kira back to our program,\Nno matter what it might take.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans in pain]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-He died!\N-[Ide] This is bad! He's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mikami...\N-[Teru] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're even better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA WANTS ROOM CHECKED FOR DEVICES.\NI'M REMOVING THEM BEFORE HE SEES THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] What? He's removing the bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] I don't understand.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can talk without any constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kiyomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kiyomi] Light is… Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I won't allow you\Nto ask Kiyomi who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll leave the rest to you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who was on the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of my followers\Nwho I've shared my power with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] I can't believe it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the only man\NI ever really admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, the only man\NI ever felt a connection with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, to find out you're Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Please, join me, Kiyomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will be\Nthe goddess of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-[men exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Kiyomi was able\Nto work things out with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided that from now on,\NI'm going to pretend to be dating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to find Kira that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Teru] Delete, delete, delete,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,delete, delete,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ending theme song playing]